sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Client (Browser)

    box rgb(240, 248, 255) Ingress Edge - Perimeter
        participant GW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>(Envoy Proxy)
        participant O2P as OAuth2-Proxy<br/>(ext_authz)
    end

    box rgb(255, 245, 238) Identity Provider
        participant IDP as Keycloak<br/>(OIDC)
    end

    box rgb(240, 255, 240) Service Mesh
        participant Mesh as Istio Proxy<br/>(App Sidecar)
        participant App as Demo App<br/>(Container)
    end

    %% Phase 1: Unauthenticated Access Attempt
    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
        Note over User, App: Phase 1: Unauthenticated Request Interception
        User->>GW: GET https://demo.example.com/
        GW->>O2P: gRPC/HTTP Check (ext_authz)<br/>Headers: No Cookie
        O2P-->>GW: HTTP 401 Unauthorized<br/>(Needs Authentication)
        GW-->>User: HTTP 302 Found<br/>Location: /oauth2/start
    end

    %% Phase 2: OIDC Authorization Code Flow
    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
        Note over User, IDP: Phase 2: OpenID Connect Authorization Code Flow
        User->>GW: GET /oauth2/start
        GW->>O2P: Forward Request (ext_authz bypassed)
        O2P-->>User: HTTP 302 Redirect to IDP
        User->>IDP: GET /auth/realms/kube-lab/protocol/openid-connect/auth...
        IDP-->>User: Present Login UI
        User->>IDP: Submit Credentials
        IDP-->>User: HTTP 302 Redirect<br/>Location: /oauth2/callback?code=XYZ
    end

    %% Phase 3: Token Exchange & Session Initialization
    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
        Note over User, IDP: Phase 3: Token Exchange & Secure Session Creation
        User->>GW: GET /oauth2/callback?code=XYZ
        GW->>O2P: Forward Callback Request
        O2P->>IDP: POST /token (Exchange 'code' for Tokens)
        IDP-->>O2P: Return ID Token & Access Token (JWT)
        Note over O2P: Encrypt tokens into a secure session cookie
        O2P-->>GW: HTTP 302 Redirect to /<br/>Set-Cookie: _oauth2_proxy=encrypted_payload...
        GW-->>User: HTTP 302 Redirect to /<br/>(with Session Cookie)
    end

    %% Phase 4: Authenticated Access & Mesh Validation
    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
        Note over User, App: Phase 4: Deep Inspection (Mesh Level)
        User->>GW: GET https://demo.example.com/<br/>Cookie: _oauth2_proxy=...

        GW->>O2P: gRPC/HTTP Check (ext_authz)<br/>Pass Cookie
        Note over O2P: Validate Session Cookie,<br/>Extract upstream Access Token (JWT)
        O2P-->>GW: HTTP 200 OK<br/>Inject Header: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

        Note over GW: Request is forwarded to the mesh with the JWT.
        GW->>Mesh: Forward Request<br/>Header: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

        Note over Mesh: 1. RequestAuthentication (Sidecar):<br/>Fetch Keycloak JWKS & verify JWT signature/expiry
        Note over Mesh: 2. AuthorizationPolicy (Sidecar):<br/>Evaluate RBAC constraints (e.g., claims[groups])

        alt User lacks required role
            Mesh-->>GW: HTTP 403 Forbidden
            Note over GW: EnvoyFilter intercepts 403 Forbidden status
            GW-->>User: Return Custom HTML "Access Denied" + Logout Button
        else User is authorized
            Note over Mesh: Request is cleared! Forwarding to local backend.
            Mesh->>App: GET / (Direct HTTP traffic)
            App-->>Mesh: HTTP 200 OK (Application Payload)
            Mesh-->>GW: HTTP 200 OK
            GW-->>User: HTTP 200 OK (Application UI rendered)
        end
    end
